LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">941.11</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n91137.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">wings</tr_> of a bat, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:76\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.76</biblScope> </bibl>; of insects, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:532a:25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">532a25</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg030:682b:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PA\">PA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">682b18</biblScope></bibl>, al. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n91137.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">any winged creature</tr_>, as the Sphinx, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg015.perseus-grc1:806\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">806</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.); a beetle, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg005.perseus-grc1:76\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pax\">Pax</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">76</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n91137.4\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">omen</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πιστὸν ἐξ ὑμῶν π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:97\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OC\">OC</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">97</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n91137.5\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">anything like wings</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">feathers</tr_>: as </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n91137.6\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">oars</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐρετμά, τά τε πτερὰ νηυσὶ πέλονται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:11:125\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.125</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">νηὸς πτερά</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:628\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Op.\">Op.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">628</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (unless <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sails</tr_>, cf. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πτίλον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:111:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">111.2</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅπῃ νεὼς στείλαιμ᾽ ἂν οὔριον π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg014.perseus-grc1:147\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hel.\">Hel.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">147